'Not again! Stop! Thief! Oh, please, please help me! That blasted cur! It loves to torment me!\n\n'The wretched thing has run off with my engagement ring. Please! You must see if you can get it back. I am absolutely terrified of the creatures and they know it!'
Unhelpful hounds can be found on the Second Tier of Minas Tirith.\n\nYou should chase the hound and retrieve the engagement ring.
